  "local_port": 59092,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Can we load money in multi wallet ICICI card?",
  "response": "Yes, you can load money into a multi-wallet ICICI card. ICICI Bank offers various prepaid and multi-wallet cards that allow you to manage and use funds across multiple digital wallets seamlessly. Here\u2019s how you can load money onto your multi-wallet ICICI card:\n\n### **1. Using ICICI Bank Net Banking:**\n- **Log in** to your ICICI Bank net banking account.\n- Navigate to the **\u2018Cards\u2019** section and select your multi-wallet ICICI card.\n- Choose the **\u2018Load/Re-load\u2019** option.\n- Enter the desired amount you wish to load onto the card.\n- **Confirm** the transaction. The funds should reflect in your card balance shortly.\n\n### **2. Via the ICICI Bank Mobile App:**\n- **Open** the ICICI Bank mobile banking app on your smartphone.\n- **Log in** using your credentials.\n- Go to the **\u2018Cards\u2019** or **\u2018Wallets\u2019** section.\n- Select your multi-wallet ICICI card.\n- Tap on the **\u2018Load\u2019** or **\u2018Re-load\u2019** option.\n- Enter the amount and **authorize** the transaction using your preferred authentication method (e.g., OTP, PIN).\n- The loaded amount will be available on your card instantly or within a few minutes.\n\n### **3. Through ICICI Branches:**\n- **Visit** the nearest ICICI Bank branch.\n- **Speak** with a bank representative and inform them that you wish to load money onto your multi-wallet ICICI card.\n- **Provide** necessary details and the amount you wish to load.\n- Complete any required documentation, and the representative will process the loading of funds onto your card.\n\n### **4. Using ATMs:**\n- **Insert** your multi-wallet ICICI card into an ICICI ATM.\n- **Enter** your PIN and navigate to the **\u2018Load Money\u2019** or **\u2018Re-load Wallet\u2019** option.\n- **Enter** the amount you wish to load and confirm the transaction.\n- The funds will be added to your card balance.\n\n### **5. Auto-Recharge Feature:**\nSome multi-wallet ICICI cards offer an **auto-recharge** feature that automatically loads funds from your linked ICICI Bank account when your balance falls below a predefined threshold. To set this up:\n- **Access** your card settings via the ICICI mobile app or net banking.\n- Navigate to the **\u2018Auto-Recharge\u2019** option.\n- **Enable** the feature and set the desired threshold and recharge amount.\n- **Confirm** the settings to activate auto-recharge.\n\n### **Tips to Consider:**\n- **Check Limits:** Be aware of the loading limits imposed on your card, which can vary based on the card type and your account status.\n- **Fees:** Some loading methods might incur fees. Review the fee structure associated with your card to avoid unexpected charges.\n- **Security:** Always ensure that you are using secure channels (official app, net banking, or branch) to load money onto your card to protect your financial information.\n\n### **Support and Assistance:**\nIf you encounter any issues or have specific questions regarding loading money onto your multi-wallet ICICI card, you can contact ICICI Bank\u2019s customer support:\n\n- **Customer Care Number:** 1860 120 7777 (available 24/7)\n- **Email Support:** [ICICI Customer Support Email](mailto:cservice@icicibank.com)\n- **Visit:** Your nearest ICICI Bank branch for in-person assistance.\n\n### **Conclusion**\nLoading money onto your multi-wallet ICICI card is a straightforward process with multiple convenient options available. Whether you prefer online methods like net banking and mobile apps or traditional approaches like visiting a branch or using ATMs, ICICI Bank ensures that you can manage your funds efficiently across various digital wallets.\n\nIf you're unsure about the specifics of your particular multi-wallet card or need assistance with a unique scenario, reaching out directly to ICICI Bank\u2019s customer service will provide tailored support based on your account and card type.",
